    <條號>Article 29</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[When relevant documents specified in these Regulations are in a foreign language, the organization must attach a Chinese translation certified by an overseas embassy or representative office or by a domestic notary public. However, if the aforementioned documents are in English, those are exempt from attaching Chinese translation certified.]]></條文內容>
