  <條文>
    <條號>Article 30</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Issuing authorities that have been commissioned by the central competent authority shall, when issuing permits or establishment approval documents, send a copy to the special municipality, county, or city competent authority where the said clearance organization or disposal site or plant is located.
Regarding the regulations in Chapter 3 on the documents that need to be permitted, approved, kept for reference, sent in as copy, or submitted, clearance or disposal organizations that had their permits or establishment approval documents issued by an authority commissioned by the central competent authority shall send these documents separately both to the issuing authority and the special municipality, county, or city competent authority where the said clearance organization or disposal site or plant is located.]]></條文內容>
