    <條號>Article 31-2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Disposal organizations shall submit a post-closure restoration plan with the paragraph 2, article 41-3 of Methods and Facilities Standards for the Storage, Clearance and Disposal of Industrial Waste within the prescribed time limit. The application shall be approved by the issuing authority and included in the disposal permit document.]]></條文內容>
